---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import ParallaxSection from '../components/ParallaxSection.astro';
import ScrollReveal from '../components/ScrollReveal.astro';
---

<Base title="首页">
  <ParallaxSection
    bgImage="/images/hero.jpg"
    headingZh="世界温州人"
    headingEn="World Wenzhou People"
    dark={true}
  >
    <p>从东海之滨到世界舞台，温州人用脚步丈量全球，以智慧与勤劳书写跨越千年的移民史诗。</p>
    <p class="en-sub">From the shores of the East China Sea to the world stage, Wenzhou people have measured the globe with their footsteps, writing an epic of migration spanning a thousand years.</p>
  </ParallaxSection>

  <ParallaxSection
    bgImage="/images/history.jpg"
    headingZh="千年迁徙"
    headingEn="A Millennium of Migration"
  >
    <ScrollReveal>
      <p>从宋代海上丝绸之路的起点，到近代遍布全球的温州侨乡网络，温州人的迁徙史就是一部浓缩的中国全球化进程。</p>
      <p class="en-sub">From the Maritime Silk Road to modern global networks, the Wenzhou migration story mirrors China's globalization.</p>
      <a href="/history" class="cta-link">探索历史 →</a>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </ParallaxSection>

  <ParallaxSection
    bgImage="/images/business.jpg"
    headingZh="商行天下"
    headingEn="Business Across Borders"
    dark={true}
  >
    <ScrollReveal>
      <p>从巴黎的皮具工坊到迪拜的贸易中心，从米兰的服装街区到圣保罗的电子市场，温州商人以敏锐的商业嗅觉闻名于世。</p>
      <p class="en-sub">From Paris to Dubai, Milan to Sao Paulo — Wenzhou entrepreneurs are known for their sharp business instincts.</p>
      <a href="/business" class="cta-link">探索商业 →</a>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </ParallaxSection>

  <ParallaxSection
    bgImage="/images/culture.jpg"
    headingZh="文化传承"
    headingEn="Culture Preserved Abroad"
  >
    <ScrollReveal>
      <p>无论身在何处，一碗糯米饭、一句温州话、一座妈祖庙，都是温州人心中不变的故乡坐标。</p>
      <p class="en-sub">Wherever they go, a bowl of sticky rice, a phrase in Wenzhou dialect, a Mazu temple — these remain the unchanging coordinates of home.</p>
      <a href="/culture" class="cta-link">探索文化 →</a>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </ParallaxSection>
</Base>

<script src="../scripts/parallax.js"></script>
<script src="../scripts/scroll-reveal.js"></script>
